sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant KRBACProxy as kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant APIServer as vLLM API Server<br/>(FastAPI/uvicorn)<br/>8000/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
    participant ZMQ as ZeroMQ IPC
    participant Engine as vLLM AsyncEngine<br/>(Scheduler)
    participant Executor as CPU Model Executor<br/>(PyTorch)
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 1: OpenAI-Compatible Inference Request

    Client->>KRBACProxy: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTPS/8443<br/>Auth: RBAC (platform)
    KRBACProxy->>APIServer: Forward<br/>HTTP/8000<br/>API Key (optional)
    APIServer->>ZMQ: Dispatch request<br/>ZeroMQ IPC (in-process)
    ZMQ->>Engine: Schedule batch
    Engine->>Executor: Execute forward pass<br/>Direct call (in-process)
    Executor->>Executor: PyTorch CPU inference<br/>PagedAttention + C++ kernels
    Executor-->>Engine: Token output
    Engine-->>ZMQ: Generation result
    ZMQ-->>APIServer: Response / SSE stream
    APIServer-->>KRBACProxy: JSON / SSE stream
    KRBACProxy-->>Client: HTTP/HTTPS Response

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 2: Model Loading (startup)

    Engine->>HFHub: GET model config + weights<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN
    HFHub-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>S3: GET model weights (alternative)<br/>HTTPS/443<br/>Auth: AWS credentials
    S3-->>Engine: Model artifacts
    Engine->>Executor: Load model into memory<br/>Direct call

    Note over Client, S3: Flow 3: gRPC Inference Request

    participant GRPCClient as gRPC Client
    participant GRPCServer as vLLM gRPC Server<br/>50051/TCP Plaintext

    GRPCClient->>GRPCServer: Inference Request<br/>gRPC/50051<br/>Plaintext (no TLS)
    GRPCServer->>ZMQ: Dispatch request<br/>ZeroMQ IPC
    ZMQ->>Engine: Schedule batch
    Engine->>Executor: Execute forward pass
    Executor-->>Engine: Token output
    Engine-->>ZMQ: Generation result
    ZMQ-->>GRPCServer: Response
    GRPCServer-->>GRPCClient: gRPC streaming response<br/>Plaintext
